milestones.description: Habibul Bashar and Rajin Saleh's 175-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 130 between Habibul Bashar and Ashraful
Habibul Bashar has scored 10 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for BAN breaking Javed Omar's record
Rajin Saleh's 108 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for BAN), surpassing Mehrab Hossain's 101
Rajin Saleh has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (64) in an innings in ODIs for BAN, going past Ashraful's 62
Habibul Bashar and Rajin Saleh's 175-run partnership is BAN's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 170 between Mehrab Hossain and Shahriar Hossain
